name: INDateSearchType
desc: Constants indicating the type of date-based search to perform.

items.name: case byDueDate
items.desc: A search type that requires matching the due date of a reminder to the specified value.

items.name: case byModifiedDate
items.desc: A search type that requires matching the modification date of a note.

items.name: case byCreatedDate
items.desc: A search type that requires matching the creation date of a note.
